Hi,

Thanks for writing to Dr. Math.

There is no "standard" ellipse with a "standard" ratio of width to
height. The circle (where the ratio is exactly 1) is the most studied
ellipse. 

Does this help?  Please feel free to write back with any questions you
may have.

